dnl Check platform (host system)
dnl ------------------------------------------------------------------------

dnl assume Unix
USE_UNIX=1
USE_LINUX=
USE_SGI=
USE_HPUX=
USE_SYSV=
USE_SVR4=
USE_AIX=
USE_SUN=
